1
00:00:54,360 --> 00:00:57,040
Your Majesty, is something bothering you?

2
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:02,520
Where is Cangyue?

3
00:01:02,760 --> 00:01:03,720
I don't know.

4
00:01:04,160 --> 00:01:05,080
These past few days,

5
00:01:05,080 --> 00:01:07,320
Lady Cangyue has been acting very mysteriously.

6
00:01:07,320 --> 00:01:10,039
I reckon she's probably been at the little prince's place.

7
00:01:10,039 --> 00:01:10,840
Insolent!

8
00:01:12,160 --> 00:01:13,160
How dare she!

9
00:01:18,440 --> 00:01:19,320
Dismissed.

10
00:01:24,960 --> 00:01:27,289
If you have the guts, don't ever come back!

11
00:01:29,600 --> 00:01:32,560
I didn't expect the protagonist of this project

12
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:34,160
to have such a tragic background.

13
00:01:34,160 --> 00:01:35,420
Feeling sorry for him?

14
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:37,800
Well,

15
00:01:37,800 --> 00:01:38,640
Not really.

16
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:41,560
I'm just a little curious.

17
00:01:45,039 --> 00:01:46,370
His Majesty died early.

18
00:01:47,960 --> 00:01:48,560
Ah, no.

19
00:01:50,039 --> 00:01:51,479
The late Emperor died early.

20
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:52,680
The Grand Princess supported His Majesty

21
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,000
after he ascended the throne at a young age,

22
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:56,000
and ruled from behind the curtain for many years.

23
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:58,240
To make him lose the support of the people,

24
00:01:58,240 --> 00:02:00,280
she indeed forced him to do many bad things.

25
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:02,080
His background is truly tragic.

26
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:04,160
But he's just an NPC.

27
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,680
No need to feel sorry for him.

28
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:10,039
But your feelings for the young prince

29
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:11,280
seem quite deep too.

30
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:13,400
Isn't he also an NPC?

31
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:18,890
He's different.

32
00:02:22,000 --> 00:02:22,880
Jingyuan.

33
00:02:34,760 --> 00:02:36,120
Why do I feel like

34
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:38,300
what you're experiencing

35
00:02:38,760 --> 00:02:41,090
isn't the lost emotion recovery project?

36
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,000
Tell me the truth.

37
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:49,040
Does this game have other ways to play

38
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:51,970
different from its public promotion?

39
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:54,440
You don't look like

40
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:58,020
someone who has lost their emotions.

41
00:03:02,280 --> 00:03:03,400
You caught me.

42
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:06,440
I have too many emotions,

43
00:03:06,440 --> 00:03:07,720
so I came here to date.

44
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:10,400
Date? With whom?

45
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:12,360
With you.

46
00:03:13,160 --> 00:03:13,880
Me?

47
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:19,560
I couldn't tell.

48
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:22,400
Miss Cangyue has very unique taste.

49
00:03:22,760 --> 00:03:23,640
Si Xingxuan.

50
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:24,480
I...

51
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:29,170
Why aren't you wearing the hairpin I gave you?

52
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:31,600
I have too many hairpins.

53
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:32,800
I can't wear them all.

54
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,460
What are you doing?

55
00:03:38,360 --> 00:03:39,360
Now they are gone.

56
00:03:39,880 --> 00:03:40,940
Can you wear it now?

57
00:03:41,760 --> 00:03:43,640
This is a gift from Jingyuan.

58
00:03:43,640 --> 00:03:44,600
A gift?

59
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:46,400
You can wear the gift he gave you,

60
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,920
but not the gift I gave you?

61
00:03:49,200 --> 00:03:50,280
That day with me,

62
00:03:50,280 --> 00:03:52,280
you were still baring your heart.

63
00:03:52,680 --> 00:03:53,640
Today you are with another man,

64
00:03:53,640 --> 00:03:56,170
drinking tea, chatting, and being romantic.

65
00:04:01,640 --> 00:04:03,760
Your Majesty, don't scare her.

66
00:04:07,160 --> 00:04:09,400
Eunuch Jingyuan is truly kind-hearted.

67
00:04:09,400 --> 00:04:10,860
No wonder he is so popular.

68
00:04:11,920 --> 00:04:13,800
If he was thrown into the celestial prison,

69
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,460
he would be even more popular.

70
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:16,529
Si Xingxuan,

71
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,320
how can you say that?

72
00:04:18,320 --> 00:04:19,649
Jing Yuan is our friend.

73
00:04:20,279 --> 00:04:22,410
Does a servant deserve to be my friend?

74
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:24,920
A servant?

75
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:26,840
If he's a servant,

76
00:04:27,200 --> 00:04:28,460
have you ever thought,

77
00:04:28,880 --> 00:04:29,880
that I am also just

78
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:30,640
a servant by your side?

79
00:04:30,640 --> 00:04:31,840
You are different.

80
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:34,620
There is no hierarchy between us.

81
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:35,980
How am I different?

82
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,490
Then what are we?

83
00:04:42,720 --> 00:04:43,760
We are partners.

84
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:48,920
So you are nothing but

85
00:04:48,920 --> 00:04:50,520
a pawn used by His Majesty.

86
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:52,400
Unlike me.

87
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:55,610
I truly wanted to be friends with Cang Yue.

88
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,800
Say one more word,

89
00:04:58,800 --> 00:05:00,120
and I will kill you.

90
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,920
Si Xingxuan, let go of me.

91
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:02,980
What are you doing?

92
00:05:03,280 --> 00:05:04,210
Let go right now.

93
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:07,200
Let go.

94
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:17,400
You're actually defending him.

95
00:05:19,640 --> 00:05:20,440
Fine.

96
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:24,360
Sister Xiaoyue.

97
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:28,170
Brother, why do you have wrinkles on your face again?

98
00:05:29,960 --> 00:05:31,400
Sister Xiaoyue, look.

99
00:05:32,760 --> 00:05:35,040
Pixiu had puppies.

100
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:45,480
But they look exactly the same.

101
00:05:45,480 --> 00:05:47,920
Yes, they look the same.

102
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:50,240
This way, even if I lose one,

103
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:52,400
I still have another.

104
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:54,920
I wish I had two brothers.

105
00:05:55,520 --> 00:05:58,120
That way, even if one dies,

106
00:05:58,120 --> 00:06:00,640
I would still have another.

107
00:06:02,880 --> 00:06:05,560
Actually, my brother is very lonely.

108
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,360
I have seen him

109
00:06:07,360 --> 00:06:10,000
spacing out in the study several times.

110
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:12,960
But since you came,

111
00:06:12,960 --> 00:06:14,560
he started smiling.

112
00:06:17,200 --> 00:06:20,600
Is he really lonely?
